data.description: Beach bungalow just a few blocks to the beach. 1,800 square feet home with lots of space. A very inviting porch as you enter the property, great place to unwind and feel the gulf breeze. Fully fenced front and back yards. Original front door and glass upon entering. Pine hardwood floors. Formal living and dining room. The home has a lot of nostalgia with nods to the past. Very favorable layout for family gatherings. Baths and bedrooms are well laid out.  Recent upgrades. New roof, Newer air conditioner, New plumbing. The big ticket items are done! You can now put your personal touches to use. Alley access to the detached garage. Family/media room off the kitchen. Home is centrally located to the Pleasure Pier and Downtown Galveston. Walk able to the Seawall, restaurants and bars. Perfect for a primary residence or short term rental. The home can accommodate multiple people and or family's.
